➜突发！上海又一所热门民办幼儿园宣布关停！许可证到期，在园幼儿将被统筹！
http://www.sohu.com/a/414802790_172239	24114
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200825/e00c3d693ca644e0833984cbe97795ba.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">震惊！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄浦区热门民办之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>闻裕顺新理念幼儿园竟然不再办学了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200825/ac4952bb66054180a1ad7106601430c6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">8月21号（上周五）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>上海市黄浦区教育局发布公告</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《告闻裕顺新理念幼儿园家长书》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200825/7aaed21a45ce4e2eaae792b519978acf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
